---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="What Amino Brief is — and what it is not.">
  <Header slot="header" />
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Gym-floor clarity. PubMed receipts.</h1>
      <p>
        Amino Brief is an independent peptide <strong>awareness</strong> site. We explain what compounds are,
        what kind of evidence exists, how to read quality docs, and how reconstitution math works.
      </p>
      <h2>What we are</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Educational briefs with evidence grades</li>
        <li>Open math tools for concentration and syringe units</li>
        <li>A small accessories shop (bac water, syringes, cases)</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>What we are not</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Not a medical practice</li>
        <li>Not a peptide pharmacy</li>
        <li>Not your coach’s secret protocol dump</li>
        <li>Not affiliated with any research-chemical brand on the homepage</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="disclaimer">
        Nothing on this site is medical advice, a diagnosis, or a treatment plan. Many research peptides are not
        FDA-approved for the uses people discuss online. Decisions about your health belong with a qualified clinician.
        Calculators are unit-conversion helpers only.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
